structure.unit: PUBLIC LAWS IN FORCE -- COURT RULES

law.history: Repealed 1976 Ky. Acts ch. 62, sec. 135, effective June 19, 1976. -- Amended 1968 Ky. Acts ch. 152, sec. 165, effective June 13, 1968. -- Created 1952 Ky. Acts ch. 18, sec. 1, effective February 25, 1952.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Court of Appeals to promulgate Rules of Civil Procedure.
